metadata.name: Love
metadata.description:
What is love?
The word meaning of love is the feeling of extreme love and devotion towards someone or something.
Looking at your spouse, job, life with love and touching it with love makes everything beautiful.
it affects our souls and our lives in a positive way.
Just like in this photo, we feel happiness up to our veins.

Artist :K.Deniz Kalayci
Camera: Canon 6D Mark II
Location : İnegöl Turkey
Date: 12/11/2021
Dimensions :6240Px 4160px 300dpi
Edition:1/1
